                            "text": "1. Alternative mortgage transaction. For purposes of this Part, an alternative mortgage transaction that meets the definition in \u00a7 1004.2(a) includes any consumer credit transaction that is secured by a mortgage, deed of trust, or other equivalent consensual security interest in a dwelling or in residential real property that includes a dwelling. The dwelling need not be the primary dwelling of the consumer. Home equity lines of credit and subordinate lien mortgages are alternative mortgage transactions for purposes of this Part to the extent they meet the definition in \u00a7 1004.2(a)."
